Label: ncit:A1
column7: An association that specifies the parent of the branch encompassing a role's domain.

Label: ncit:A10
column7: An association created to allow the source CDRH to assign a parent to each concept with the intent of creating a hierarchy that includes only terms in which they are the contributing source.

Label: ncit:A11
column7: An association created to allow the source NICHD to assign a parent to each concept with the intent of creating a hierarchy that includes only terms in which they are a contributing source.

Label: ncit:A12
column7: An association created to relate a data element concept to the codelist term that is used to bundle its subset of valid value concepts.

Label: ncit:A13
column7: An association that indicates that a finding or lab test is related to a gene, possibly through a variant or product.

Label: ncit:A14
column7: An association that indicates that a neoplastic disease can have the characteristics defined by a Neoplasm by Special Category concept.

Label: ncit:A15
column7: An association created to allow the source CTCAE 5.0 to assign a parent to each concept with the intent of creating a hierarchy that includes only terms in which CTCAE is the contributing source.

Label: ncit:A16
column7: An association created to allow the source INC to assign a parent to each concept with the intent of creating a hierarchy that includes only terms in which they are the contributing source.

Label: ncit:A17
column7: An association that specifies the physical conditions describing the molecular form of a product. The target value should belong to the EDQM-HC State of Matter Terminology.

Label: ncit:A18
column7: An association that specifies the category of the pharmaceutical dose form, used to group together related pharmaceutical dose forms. The target value should belong to the EDQM-HC Basic Dose Form Terminology.

Label: ncit:A19
column7: An association that specifies the methods by which a pharmaceutical product is intended to be administered to the patient. The target value should belong to the EDQM-HC Administration Method Terminology.

Label: ncit:A2
column7: An association that specifies the parent of the branch encompassing the role's range.

Label: ncit:A20
column7: An association that specifies the general body sites at which a pharmaceutical product is intended to be administered. The target value should belong to the EDQM-HC Intended Site of Administration Terminology.

Label: ncit:A21
column7: An association that specifies the timing by which an active ingredient is made available in the body after administration of the pharmaceutical product, in comparison with a conventional, direct release of the active ingredient. The target value should belong to the EDQM-HC Release Characteristics Terminology.

Label: ncit:A22
column7: An association that specifies the procedures that are carried out in order to convert a manufactured item that requires such a procedure into a pharmaceutical product. The target value should belong to the EDQM-HC Transformation Terminology.

Label: ncit:A23
column7: An association that specifies one of three data types for a particular variable, String, Code or Number.

Label: ncit:A24
column7: An association that indicates a PCDC AML concept is a Authorized Value for a PCDC AML Variable concept.

Label: ncit:A25
column7: An association that specifies the paired ‘Test or Parameter Name’ codelist that goes with the ‘Test or Parameter Code’ codelist. This association uni-directionally points from a Test/Parameter Code Codelist to the Test/Parameter Name Codelist.

Label: ncit:A26
column7: An association that shows which PCDC AML Authorized Values are possible for a specific Variable.

Label: ncit:A27
column7: An association connecting a CTDC Property concept to its dedicated value concept(s).

Label: ncit:A28
column7: An association that indicates a PCDC EWS concept is a Authorized Value for a specific PCDC EWS Variable concept.

Label: ncit:A29
column7: An association that shows which Authorized Values are possible for a specific PCDC EWS Variable concept.

Label: ncit:A3
column7: An association that specifies that a role exists as part of a role hierarchy and specifies the role's parent, the role that this role specializes.

Label: ncit:A30
column7: An association connecting an ICDC Property concept to its dedicated value concept(s).

Label: ncit:A31
column7: An association that connects a concept representing a GDC property to its dedicated value concept(s).

Label: ncit:A32
column7: An association that that connects a concept representing a GDC value to any associated GDC property concept(s).

Label: ncit:A33
column7: An association that indicates a concept is a dedicated Authorized Value concept for a specific PCDC GCT Variable.

Label: ncit:A34
column7: An association that shows which Authorized Values are possible for a specific PCDC GCT Variable.

Label: ncit:A35
column7: An association that indicates a PCDC ALL concept is a Authorized Value for a PCDC ALL Variable concept.

Label: ncit:A36
column7: An association that shows which PCDC ALL Authorized Values are possible for a specific Variable.

Label: ncit:A37
column7: An association that shows which Authorized Values are possible for a specific SeroNet Variable.

Label: ncit:A38
column7: An association that shows which Authorized Values are possible for a specific PCDC OS Variable.

Label: ncit:A39
column7: An association that shows which Authorized Values are possible for a specific PCDC HL Variable.

Label: ncit:A4
column7: An association that indicates the property or association that the qualifier is to be used with.

Label: ncit:A40
column7: An association that shows which Authorized Values are possible for a specific DIPG/DMG Variable.

Label: ncit:A41
column7: An association that specifies the physical form of the medication when the drug is administered to the patient.

Label: ncit:A42
column7: An association specifying the Values for a specific OORO Prostate Cancer (PC) Attribute.

Label: ncit:A43
column7: An association specifying the Values for a specific OORO Head and Neck Cancer (HNC) Attribute.

Label: ncit:A44
column7: An association specifying the Values for a specific OORO Breast Cancer (BC) Attribute.

Label: ncit:A45
column7: An association specifying the Values for a specific OORO Lung Cancer (LC) Attribute

Label: ncit:A46
column7: An association that specifies one of three data types for a particular variable, String, Code or Number.

Label: ncit:A48
column7: An association that shows which Authorized Values are possible for a specific ACC/AHA SARS2 Variable.

Label: ncit:A5
column7: An association that connects the salt form of a drug with its free acid or free base.

Label: ncit:A6
column7: An association that connects the salt form of a drug with its free acid or free base.

Label: ncit:A7
column7: An association that connects a drug or other agent to a clinically intended, molecular-scale target. The target value may be a gene, gene product, anatomic structure, cell, biological process, or other concept, where the effect of the agent on the target is thought to be of therapeutic, diagnostic, or other clinical relevance to a disease process. The effect is most often direct, as defined at a molecular scale, but may also be indirect and/or defined at a larger scale.

Label: ncit: Association property A8
column7: An association that connects the concept defining a particular terminology subset with concepts that belong to this subset.

Label: ncit: Association property A9
column7: An association that is asserted when there is a relationship or association between the therapeutic moiety and the endogenous gene product.
